parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of airbags can lead to serious injuries or fatalities in the event of an accident.
symptoms: Airbags did not deploy in a crash
airbag light stays on
passenger airbag light comes on when weight is applied to the passenger seat
seatbelt warning light is on
and failure to latch seatbelts.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Brake failure can cause accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: Brake pads were suspected of failing
rust built up on calipers
brake fluid leak
and failure to stop the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The Takata airbag recall can lead to serious injuries or fatalities due to the risk of exploding airbag inflators.
symptoms: Notification of Takata airbag recall
parts not available for repair
and long wait times for repair.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Seatbelt issues can lead to injuries or fatalities in the event of an accident.
symptoms: Backseat seatbelt female receptacle will not latch to the male end
and failure to buckle up.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Corrosion of Rear ABS Sensor and Wiring Harness
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The corrosion of the rear ABS sensor and wiring harness can cause the ABS system to malfunction, leading to extended stopping distances, loss of traction, and increased risk of accidents.
symptoms: ABS and brake warning lights illuminate
intermittent or permanent loss of ABS functionality
vibration or pulsing sensation when braking
and reduced braking performance.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake system can cause loss of braking performance, leading to accidents, injuries, and fatalities.
symptoms: Spongy brake pedal
delayed or incomplete braking response
grinding or screeching noises when braking
and inability to stop the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the ABS system can cause loss of traction, extended stopping distances, and increased risk of accidents.
symptoms: ABS and brake warning lights illuminate
intermittent or permanent loss of ABS functionality
vibration or pulsing sensation when braking
and reduced braking performance.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Unintended acceleration can cause loss of vehicle control, accidents, and injuries, potentially leading to fatalities.
symptoms: Sudden acceleration without warning
stuck accelerator pedal
failure to slow down or stop
surging or jerking of the vehicle
and difficulty steering.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Brake failure can cause loss of vehicle control, accidents, and injuries, potentially leading to fatalities.
symptoms: Failure to slow down or stop
ABS light and brake light coming on
difficulty slowing down
and sudden acceleration.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Throttle Sensor and Engine Wiring Harness Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Failure of the throttle sensor and engine wiring harness can cause the vehicle to stall, leading to a loss of power and potentially causing accidents.
symptoms: Vehicle stalling
check engine light illuminating
and failure to resume normal function after restarting the engine.
